race.comment: AMLETO (5) looks well placed here third up. Both runs this time in have been rock solid, finding the line nicely at Caulfield in a BM80 behind a progressive mare in Blindedbythelight. He should be set to peak out to 2040m now and is open to further improvement from a nice draw. SO BRAVE (4) is another horse with upside having won well at big odds fresh before a good effort behind the in-form Zambardo second up. Fitter again now and should take beating. SAXON BEAUTY (10) is racing in career best form, just finding one better at her past couple, trying hard in the Pinker Pinker Plate last time out. She'll roll forward from the wide draw and take catching. FAREWELL TO EIRE (11) was better here last time and will just need a good ride from the wide gate to be figuring. HOT TOO GO (13) was poor last time but can improve.
